        <abstract> 
<p>The almond-tree TR gave him produced no fruit, but the Chinese double peach has three. Asks for ripe almond fruits and any <hi rend="italic">odd</hi> peaches, to compare the stones.</p> 
            <p>Asks about modification in fruit or foliage in any fruit-trees from being grafted,</p>
            <p>and about seedlings of pears and wheat said to have been found in hedges and woods.</p>
        </abstract>
